 Z_{1,1} = \sum_{k=1}^n X_{1,k}Y_{k,1} = \sum_{k=1}^{n/2}X_{1,k}Y_{k,1} + \sum_{k=n/2+1}^{n} X_{1,k}Y_{k,1} =\\ \sum_{k=1}^{n/2} A_{1,k}E_{k,1} + \sum_{k=1}^{n/2} B_{1,k}G_{k,1} = (AE)_{1,1} + (BG)_{1,1} 
